data.description: Wow! Fantastic 2nd floor  Turn Key condo with high ceilings open light and bright layout with easy access for food service great for entertaining. Large bedrooms one with sliders to specious screen lanai area overlooking expansive swimming pool cabana and manicured Tropical landscapes. Amazing large double bathroom with shared, tub shower.Each bath has toilet & full size vanity  Nice living dining combo very versatile with furniture placement choices. This darling unit has eat at counter and eat in kitchen, indoor laundry with appliances, lots of natural sunlight makes this such a tranquil unit nestled into the most populated area of town close to Rumrunners & Lady Lobster restaurant.  Walk to publix shopping and popular restaurants. Don't miss this Fabulous must sell.  Comes fully furnished. Fantastic vacation rental, furnished heated pool . Special Remarks
